e the use of nano-engineered\nsurfaces as enhanced photocathodes, providing a robust, air-stable source of\nhigh average current electron beams with great potential for industrial and\nscientific applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 00:02:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Mar 2023 08:48:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
