r night or season) the results from mid-infrared\nobservations will remain the same to the zeroth order which is an advantage\nover reflected light observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 12:44:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2023 10:06:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Apr 2023 11:37:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-04"}
