d by CM to obtain the complete variances from\ntruncated pdfs and show that it imposes stringent conditions on the kurtosis\ncoefficients that allow to determine them accurately. We also provide a\ndemonstration of a qualitative change of regime in the updown wind asymmetry of\nthe wave-slope probability when the wind speed increases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 13:54:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
